        <div>
          <head rend="italic"><hi rend="roman">Desperato's</hi> Banquet.</head> <!-- variant: Desperato's Banquet.] [] S5983 -->
            <notatedMusic>
            <!-- MEI goes here -->
          </notatedMusic>
          <ab>
            <supplied reason="underlay">
            <stage type="voice" rend="italic">For a Basse alone.</stage> <!-- variant: For a Basse alone.] An Attendant sings in a base. S5983 -->
          <lg type="stanza">
            <l rend="indent2">COme heavy Souls, oppressed with the weight</l>
            <l rend="indent2">of crimes, or pangs, or want of your delight;</l>
            <l rend="indent3">come <seg xml:id="v1">drown</seg> in <hi rend="italic">Lethes</hi> sleepy Lake,</l> <!-- variants: drown] down S5983; Lethes] Lethe's, S5983 -->
            <l rend="indent4">what ever makes you ake;</l>
            <l rend="indent4">drink healths from poys'ned bowls,</l> <!-- variant: healths] health S5983 -->
            <l>breath out your cares together with your Souls;</l>
            <l rend="indent5">cool death's a salve</l>
            <l rend="indent5">that all may have,</l> <!-- variant: that] Which S5983 -->
            <l rend="indent2">ther's no distinction in the Grave.</l>
          </lg> <!-- variant: no stanza break S5983 -->
          <lg type="stanza">
            <l rend="indent1">Lay down your loads before death's Iron door;</l>
            <l>sigh, and sigh out, groan once, and groan no more.</l>
          </lg>
        </supplied>
        </ab>
        </div>
